      <h3>Life transition support</h3>
      <p>For immigration adjustment, relocation, identity shifts, and major life changes that make you ask, “Who am I now?”</p>
      <ul class="check-list">
        <li>Clarify the transition</li>
        <li>Map stressors and supports</li>
        <li>Create small next steps</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Work and meaning coaching</h3>
      <p>For people who are successful on paper but feel disconnected from the work they do every day.</p>
      <ul class="check-list">
        <li>Values-based career reflection</li>
        <li>Decision support</li>
        <li>Action plans between sessions</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Therapy-informed growth work</h3>
      <p>For stress, overthinking, low motivation, relationship patterns, and the feeling that you are “just pushing through.”</p>
      <ul class="check-list">
        <li>Pattern recognition</li>
        <li>Emotional language</li>
        <li>Practical coping tools</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
